title: Zuckerberg Looks to Deliver Hit to Musk With Upcoming Twitter Clone
description: The planned Meta microblogging app is seen as a potential rival because of the Instagram connection and the company’s history.

title: China Restricts Exports of Two Metals Used in High-Performance Chips
description: Industry executives see Beijing’s export ban on gallium and germanium as retaliation over chip curbs by the U.S. and others.

title: China's Chip Industry Grim but Defiant as New U.S. Sanctions Loom
description: At an annual semiconductor-industry conference in Shanghai, U.S. export restrictions are a major topic.

title: Zuckerberg's Quest to Re-Enter China Faces Challenge: His Own Words
description: More than a decade after Beijing blocked Facebook, parent Meta’s effort to sell its virtual-reality headsets in China faces challenges that include some of the founder’s past comments.
